column5: Spent the weekend at the river,That place is a zoo on the weekends.Hundreds of boats,but not to many fishing for these Giants
Very nice, as far as bass go  Way to go
Way to go Steve,   I haven't seen you around at the club.
Who needs steelhead when you can get monster smallies like that. Amazing !
Sweet fish for the river!  Nice shots.
You cant beat those fall smallies! Great Haul from the river!
Beautiful Smallies but for most anglers that fish the Niagara River this time of year those are NOT adequate replacements for steelhead
WOW beast smallmouths! awesome report and fish
I'd be on one of the other boats too. Lol those big sunfish are nice but chrome is where the heart is! Nice fish though!
